title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon Spotlight - Airbus H125 - version 1.3.4
description:
In this video we look at the latest version of Airbus H125 received after the initial beta version. The helicopter received some really nice updates including the option to add passengers and bagage to the helicopter. In addition to that an ambulance heli livery is added to the helicopter so you can now also fly patients if you want.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/25212/airbus-h125-helicopter-project
